#WeArePalmSprings Meet Randy Buckmaster, the Manager of Palm Springs Windmill Tours. 
Palm Springs Windmill Tours is the only windmill tour that goes behind the gates onto a working windmill farm, allowing you to explore historical exhibits and learn about the evolution of wind energy in the Coachella Valley. They are currently offering self-driving tours. Watch the video to learn more!
